In the INTEREST OF B.P., Minor Child, K.D., Mother, Appellant, J.M., Father, Appellant. No. 19-0233 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

A father and mother appeal separately from the juvenile court order terminating their parental rights. AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.

AFFIRMED ON BOTH APPEALS.
